<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,151,383]" pageId="2" pageNumber="65">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,327,151,175]" pageId="2" pageNumber="65">Discussion:</emphasis>
The new species has characteristics of both 
<taxonomicName box="[802,940,152,175]" class="Insecta" family="Notodontidae" genus="Platychasma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
